text: Amblymora elongata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1943. It is known from the Celebes Islands.BioLib.cz - Amblymora elongata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1943
